or more. We offer the special rate of $12 per person. Each person paid for will receive two hours of unlimited bowling and shoe rental.  Lane Reservation  Lane Reservations are available but must be made for a minimum of 2 lanes for an hour or 1 lane for two hours. The cost is $40 per lane per hour for guest reservations. It is recommended to have no more than 5 bowlers per lane to maximize the value of the package.          Bowling & Billiards    Back to main content           Hours    Rates and Reservations    Specials                  UIC Logo        Student Centers         Quick Links    Staff Directory    Student Employment    Feedback      Resources    Lockers Info and Policy    Bicycle Repair    Donation Bins      Tools    Building Directory    BM Reports    Operations Reports        BUTTON    Policies    Sustainability    Hours & Locations         Contact   scenters@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 